  "html": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><table class=\"infobox\" style=\"min-width:22em;max-width:32em;border-collapse:separate;border-spacing:3px\"><tbody><tr><th colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center;font-size:125%;font-weight:bold;font-weight:bold; background: none; line-height: 1.1em;\"><table style=\"width:100%\"><tbody><tr><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:left;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:middle;text-align:center;padding:0px 7px 5px 7px\">Myrmadora Haen</td><td style=\"border:none;vertical-align:top;text-align:right;width:50px\"><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\"><img alt=\"Lys.svg\" src=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/50px-Lys.svg.png\" width=\"50\" height=\"50\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/75px-Lys.svg.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/f/fd/Lys.svg/100px-Lys.svg.png 2x\" /></a></td></tr></tbody></table></th></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" class=\"infobox-image\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<a href=\"/index.php/File:Myrmadora_Haen_by_Riotarttherite.png\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"Myrmadora Haen by Riotarttherite.png\" src=\"/images/thumb/d/dc/Myrmadora_Haen_by_Riotarttherite.png/300px-Myrmadora_Haen_by_Riotarttherite.png\" width=\"300\" height=\"400\" srcset=\"/images/thumb/d/dc/Myrmadora_Haen_by_Riotarttherite.png/450px-Myrmadora_Haen_by_Riotarttherite.png 1.5x, /images/thumb/d/dc/Myrmadora_Haen_by_Riotarttherite.png/600px-Myrmadora_Haen_by_Riotarttherite.png 2x\" /></a><div>Myrmadora Haen by Riotarttherite</div></td></tr><tr><td colspan=\"2\" style=\"text-align:center\">\n<hr /></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Allegiance</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/House_Haen\" title=\"House Haen\">House Haen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Culture</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lyseni</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Born</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/103_AC\" title=\"103 AC\">103</a>–<a href=\"/index.php/133_AC\" title=\"133 AC\">133&#160;AC</a><sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Died</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a><br /><a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lys</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Father</th><td>\n<a href=\"/index.php/Torreo_Haen\" title=\"Torreo Haen\">Torreo Haen</a></td></tr><tr><th scope=\"row\">Book</th><td>\n<i><a href=\"/index.php/Fire_%26_Blood\" title=\"Fire &amp; Blood\">Fire &amp; Blood</a></i> (mentioned)</td></tr></tbody></table>\n<p><b>Myrmadora Haen</b> was a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lyseni</a> noblewoman of <a href=\"/index.php/House_Haen\" title=\"House Haen\">House Haen</a>, a possible marriage candidate for King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III Targaryen</a>.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"History\">History</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Myrmadora_Haen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=1\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: History\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<p>Myrmadora was the daughter of <a href=\"/index.php/Torreo_Haen\" title=\"Torreo Haen\">Torreo Haen</a>, a <a href=\"/index.php/Lys\" title=\"Lys\">Lyseni</a> <a href=\"/index.php/Magister\" title=\"Magister\">magister</a>. She attended the <a href=\"/index.php/Maiden%27s_Day_Ball\" title=\"Maiden&#39;s Day Ball\">Maiden's Day Ball</a> wearing a gown of translucent blue-green silk that matched her eyes, with only a jeweled girdle underneath. The dress shocked others, but the <a href=\"/index.php/Kingsguard\" title=\"Kingsguard\">Kingsguard</a> barred her from King <a href=\"/index.php/Aegon_III_Targaryen\" title=\"Aegon III Targaryen\">Aegon III</a>'s throne room until she changed clothes.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_2-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabunder_the_regents_-_war_and_peace_and_cattle_shows.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-2\">&#91;2&#93;</a></sup>\n</p><p>In <a href=\"/index.php/135_AC\" title=\"135 AC\">135&#160;AC</a>, Myrmadora was <a href=\"/index.php/Poison\" title=\"Poison\">poisoned</a> along with her mother, sister(s), father, her father's siblings, and her father's supporters at the feast he held to celebrate his becoming <a href=\"/index.php/First_Magister\" title=\"First Magister\">First Magister</a> of Lys.<sup id=\"cite_ref-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D_3-0\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-Rfabthe_lysene_spring_and_the_end_of_regency.7B.7B.7B3.7D.7D.7D.7B.7B.7B4.7D.7D.7D-3\">&#91;3&#93;</a></sup>\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Family\">Family</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=Myrmadora_Haen&amp;action=edit&amp;section=2\" class=\"tw-editsection-onhover\" title=\"Edit section: Family\"><span class=\"glyphicon glyphicon-pencil\"></span> </a><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">]</span></span></h2>\n<div style=\"overflow:auto;\"><table cellspacing=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" border=\"0\" style=\"border-collapse:separate;font: 90% sans-serif;\">\n<tbody><tr align=\"center\"><td rowspan=\"2\" colspan=\"2\"><div style=\"width:2em; height:2em;\"><s